{"ts": "2026-06-08T03:51:47.194496+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Setup & Day-to-Day Development Commands\n\nThis is a **Vue 3 + Vite** starter template using **pnpm** as the package manager.\n\n### Prerequisites\n- **Node.js**: `v24` (specified in `.nvmrc`)\n- **Package manager**: `pnpm` (enforced via the `preinstall` script — `npm`/`yarn` are blocked)\n\n---\n\n### 1. Install / Project Setup\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\nThe `preinstall` hook runs `npx only-allow pnpm` to ensure pnpm is used.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Dev Server (hot-reload)\n```bash\npnpm run dev\n```\nRuns the Vite dev server with HMR.\n\n---\n\n### 3. Build (production)\n```bash\npnpm run build\n```\nCompiles and minifies for production using `vite build`.\n\nYou can also **build and preview** the production output locally:\n```bash\npnpm run build-preview\n```\n(Equivalent to `vite build && vite preview`)\n\nOr just **preview** a previously built production bundle:\n```bash\npnpm run preview\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Unit Tests\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit\n```\nRuns unit tests via **Vitest**.\n\nFor a single run with coverage:\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit-coverage\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. Lint\n```bash\npnpm run lint\n```\nLints all `.vue`, `.ts`, and `.js` files with **ESLint**.\n\nTo automatically fix linting errors:\n```bash\npnpm run lint-fix\n```\n\n---\n\n### Bonus: Pre-commit Hooks\nThe project uses **Husky** + **lint-staged** (see `.husky/` and `lint-staged.config.js`). The `prepare` script (`husky`) sets up Git hooks automatically after `pnpm install`, so linting runs on staged files before each commit.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 744, "prompt_tokens": 4816, "total_tokens": 5560, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 321, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 4352}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 4352, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 464}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "5e6fbc6d-22fb-4a07-ac3b-95992649a290", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea55b-74d5-7543-a565-e0616faf8351-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 4816, "output_tokens": 744, "total_tokens": 5560, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 4352}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 321}}}}]}}}
